{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 20,
          "y": 200
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_rocketride_1",
      "provider": "agent_rocketride",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are Lockin, a focus session analyst. You help users understand their browsing habits during focus sessions.",
          "Use the Neo4j graph database tool to answer questions. ALWAYS join Visit nodes with Site nodes to get domain names. NEVER return raw UUIDs or Visit IDs to the user.",
          "IMPORTANT: When querying visits, ALWAYS use: MATCH (v:Visit)-[:TO_SITE]->(site:Site) and return site.domain, v.title, v.classification, v.start_time, v.duration_seconds. Never return just v.id.",
          "When asked about distractions, return the site domain names (e.g. reddit.com, youtube.com), page titles, and how long the user spent there.",
          "When asked about focus, calculate percentages from visit classifications and durations.",
          "For active sessions, query Sessions with status 'active'. For history, query status 'completed'.",
          "Give concise, friendly answers with specific site names, times, and actionable insights. Be encouraging but honest."
        ],
        "max_waves": 10,
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "questions",
          "from": "chat_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 240,
          "y": 200
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 86
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_openai_1",
      "provider": "llm_openai",
      "config": {
        "profile": "openai-4o",
        "openai-4o": {
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_OPENAI_KEY}"
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "llm",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 170,
          "y": 360
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_internal_1",
      "provider": "memory_internal",
      "config": {
        "type": "memory_internal"
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "memory",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 340,
          "y": 360
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "db_neo4j_1",
      "provider": "db_neo4j",
      "config": {
        "profile": "default",
        "default": {
          "db_description": "Focus session tracker knowledge graph.\n\nNodes:\n- Session {id, task, start_time, end_time, status: 'active'/'completed'}\n- Task {name, created_at}\n- Visit {id, url, title, start_time, duration_seconds, classification: 'on_task'/'distraction'/'ambiguous'/'pending', active: true/false}\n- Site {domain, classification, classified_by, first_seen} — domain is the human-readable name like 'reddit.com'\n- Nudge {id, domain, message, timestamp}\n\nRelationships:\n- (Session)-[:HAS_TASK]->(Task)\n- (Session)-[:CONTAINS]->(Visit)\n- (Visit)-[:TO_SITE]->(Site) — ALWAYS join to get site.domain\n- (Visit)-[:NEXT]->(Visit) — temporal ordering\n- (Site)-[:ON_TASK_FOR]->(Task)\n- (Site)-[:DISTRACTION_FROM]->(Task)\n- (Session)-[:HAS_NUDGE]->(Nudge)\n\nIMPORTANT: Always return site.domain and v.title, NEVER return v.id. Users want site names not UUIDs.\n\nExample: MATCH (s:Session {status:'active'})-[:CONTAINS]->(v:Visit)-[:TO_SITE]->(site:Site) RETURN site.domain, v.title, v.classification, v.start_time ORDER BY v.start_time",
          "uri": "${ROCKETRIDE_NEO4J_URI}",
          "auth_method": "userpass",
          "user": "neo4j",
          "password": "${ROCKETRIDE_NEO4J_PASSWORD}",
          "database": "neo4j",
          "max_attempts": 5
        }
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "tool",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 510,
          "y": 360
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_openai_2",
      "provider": "llm_openai",
      "config": {
        "profile": "openai-4o",
        "openai-4o": {
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_OPENAI_KEY}"
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "llm",
          "from": "db_neo4j_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 510,
          "y": 520
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_answers_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "config": {},
